        "gg2fiKAtE2B_text": "<p>Here’s what real women have to say about the mask that fits their lifestyle:</p>",
        "gg8pKjt6M-e_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png",
        "ggBAw8876yL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://niforashop.com/cdn/shop/files/SnapInsta.to_540424587_18020332571746546_7277520050811712452_n.jpg?v=1764087745",
        "ggL050P13q3_label": "<p>SHOP NOW</p>",
        "ggLIgSX9VHl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png",
        "ggOKNXI3QFQ_text": "Your Glow-Up Starts Here — Just Like Theirs",
        "ggPRjcYxMnL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://niforashop.com/cdn/shop/files/Screenshot_2164.png?v=1764087967",
        "ggScr007rpc_text": "<p>\"I didn’t expect much, but wow… I actually woke up with hydrated lips for the first time in years. No more dry mouth or cracking.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>- Sarah M</strong></p>",
        "ggYOx1LcoHi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://niforashop.com/cdn/shop/files/Screenshot_2165.png?v=1764087878",
        "ggYRiJJWhdb_text": "<p>\"I’ve tried regular mouth tape before and hated the feeling. This one is on another level — super soft, breathable, and doesn’t irritate my skin. Love the collagen patch in the middle too\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>- Kath</strong></p>",
        "gghJLturVVa_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png",
        "ggjT6sGLgBN_text": "<p>“I wasn’t sure about mouth tape at first, but I gave it a try and I’m so glad I did. It’s gentle, comfy, and actually makes a difference. Highly recommend!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>- Olivia</strong></p>",
        "ggsFqCa194a_text": "<p>\"I bought this mainly for snoring, and it REALLY helped. My partner says I’m so much quieter. Plus my lips look smoother in the morning — bonus!”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>- Danielle R</strong></p>",
        "gguh-2QsJA8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png",
        "ggwkxXE4jR7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://niforashop.com/cdn/shop/files/01896d46e046bdfe8dee49082b1e8e2b.jpg?v=1764175593"
