        "checksum": "28fef12274163492b5373bc61a91e018d99ce9fde9d7717c2ee33c2dffe88bec_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p>This is the most important part. I learned that mouth breathing actually keeps your body in a state of stress (\"fight or flight\") all night, preventing you from fully shutting down.<br>By forcing nasal breathing, <strong>this tape increases oxygen intake and signals your nervous system to relax.</strong> It pushes you into deep REM sleep much faster. I’m not just waking up less groggy; <strong>I’m waking up with lower cortisol levels and actual energy. This is where the real body repair—and \"beauty sleep\"—happens.</strong></p>",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. It Doesn't Hurt To Take Off",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_9_d8488d5d-47eb-4661-abe7-7bc8e3459cd9.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/7_9.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/7_9.png",
        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p><strong>UPDATE:</strong> The Collagen Mouth Tape is currently in stock, but inventory is moving fast. Check the link below to see if it's available.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Eleanor Brooks | London, UK<br>December 7, 2025</p>",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. It Helps Smooth Lip Lines",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p>It’s always annoying to buy a new product and hate it. <strong>Nifora offers a risk-free trial, so if you find it uncomfortable or don't see a difference, you aren't stuck with it.</strong> For me, the better sleep and smoother skin are worth it.</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6. The Quality of My Sleep Has Completely Changed",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p>My biggest worry was that it would hurt to peel off in the morning. Because of the collagen infusion, <strong>the adhesive is actually very gentle.</strong> It stays on all night without issues, but in the morning, <strong>it peels off easily without pulling my skin or leaving red marks.</strong></p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. No More Dry Throat in the Morning",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. You Can Try It Risk-Free",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "Discover why 40,000+ women are waking up to Better Sleep and Plumper Lips with this Hydrolyzed Collagen Mouth Tape",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p>I realized this isn't just a sleep aid; <strong>it’s doing three jobs at once.</strong> First, my jawline is getting visible again! <strong>It improves my face posture by keeping my jaw in the right position all night.</strong> Second, while it’s holding that structure, <strong>the collagen is actively treating my skin.</strong> And third, because I’m finally getting deep, restorative sleep, <strong>I wake up feeling genuinely healthy and energized.</strong> It’s rare to find one product that tackles posture, skincare, and health simultaneously.</p>",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/14_f80008c3-2301-4dd6-8cc9-ec0fc76f212e.png",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/14_f80008c3-2301-4dd6-8cc9-ec0fc76f212e.png",
        "ggWic5B8SZG_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/14_3ba448f7-4a84-46d3-af45-6033c186a8bb.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/8_5_23f4496c-434f-4f47-bb12-c6ce8f7eab62.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/8_5.png",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/8_5.png",
        "ggZHuYgoc8x_text": "1. It’s Collagen Skincare, Not Just Tape",
        "ggfwG-WQa7r_text": "<p>That’s when I found this brand, unlike harsh medical tapes, they created a <strong>Hydrolyzed Collagen</strong> version that actively hydrates your skin while you wear it.</p><p>I’m usually skeptical of viral products, but I decided to put this to the test for a week.</p>",
        "gggTy2IY0Ux_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/banner.png",
        "gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/hf_20260306_033439_004a2925-257b-4673-991c-18847ad58daf.jpg",
        "gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/6_8.png",
