        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_12.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_12.png",
        "ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_12_50193272-513c-40d6-8a84-526e705d46b1.png",
        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p>Most mouth tapes are just sticky plastic or paper that can irritate your skin. <strong>Nifora’s strips are infused with Hydrolyzed Collagen,</strong> meaning the particles are small enough to actually sink in while you sleep. <strong>It works like a targeted sheet mask that hydrates the area for 8 hours straight.</strong> So instead of just holding my mouth shut, I’m waking up with that delicate skin feeling softer and plumper.</p>",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_8_bfecaf0b-d088-4b11-aa79-fb3a06b98d45.png",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_13.png",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_13.png",
        "ggxpEEAWkOo_text": "<p>We’ve all woken up with a dry, scratchy throat or needing water immediately. I realized this was because I was breathing through my mouth all night. Since using the tape,<strong> I breathe through my nose, which naturally filters and moistens the air.</strong> I wake up feeling much fresher, and my mouth doesn't feel like sandpaper anymore.</p>",
        "ggxwUzin72S_text": "<p>I noticed recently that I was waking up with faint vertical lines above my lip—mostly from my face being squashed against the pillow or my mouth hanging open. Because <strong>this tape holds the skin in place and delivers collagen to the area, it acts like a patch.</strong> After a few nights, the skin around my mouth definitely <strong>looked smoother and less \"creased\" in the morning.</strong></p>",
        "ggy5Uy9f896_text": "<p>I’ll be honest—I used to scroll right past the mouth taping trend. It looked uncomfortable. But then I realized it’s actually a <strong>3-in-1 powerhouse: it fixes your sleep, sharpens your jawline, and prevents lip wrinkles all at once.</strong></p>"
